vent as a TDE. We also consider the TDE candidate population as a whole,\nwhich, for certain host galaxy or SMBH characteristics, is distinguishable\nstatistically from non-TDEs, suggesting that at least some TDE candidates do in\nfact arise from SMBH-disrupted stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 19:48:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 20:51:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-22"}
