during a short\nexcursion from the soft to the intermediate state. After traveling with\nconstant speed, the first component underwent a strong deceleration, which was\ncovered with unprecedented detail and suggested that MAXI J1348-630 could be\nlocated inside a low-density cavity in the interstellar medium, as already\nproposed for XTE J1550-564 and H1743-322.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 21:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
