}\\rangle_t$ respectively approaches $-0.25$ and\n$0.5$ in the thermodynamic limit; (iv) The nearest-neighbor entanglement\nacquires a finite plateau value that increases with increasing $g$, and\napproaches a saturated value $\\sim0.125$ for $g\\gg1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 13:14:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 May 2021 10:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-11"}
